snippet.title: Phobies - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Phobies is a tactical card collecting strategy game where players battle one another in the surreal realm of the subconscious, where fears manifest. Use devious tactics and unleash a dazzling array of attacks and abilities to achieve victory!

Learn more: https://www.phobies.com
Join our Discord: https://bit.ly/3AoE2xH
